   ‚ĖĎ‚Ėí‚Ėď‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ĖÄ ‚ĖĄ‚ĖÄ  ‚ĖÄ‚Ėď‚ĖÄ     Release notes:
        ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ‚ĖĄ
        ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą   Security Engineering addresses the problem of inadequate and
        ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą   incomplete security solutions. The configuration of an
        ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą   integrated and resilient security framework is the goal of
        ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą   this course on Security Engineering. In this course,
        ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą   Security Engineering, you will learn the use of security
        ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą   models and gain the ability to develop and deploy a robust
        ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą   security solution tailored for your organization. First, you
        ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą   will learn about the traditional security approaches. Next,
        ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą   you will discover security challenges with modern
        ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą   technology. Finally, you will explore how to manage and
        ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą   operate a security program. When you're finished with this
        ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą   course, you will have the skills and knowledge of security
        ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą   engineering needed to design and deploy an enterprise-wide
        ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą   security solution.
